lyrics:
[Verse]
Dawid's stacking shelves with tools, a handyman he'll be
Rudolf fixing gutters, always busy as a bee
The courier's in a rush, doesn't speak Polish, it seems
In this country town, where dreams chase their schemes

[Chorus]
Dawid and Rudolf, with their tasks to do
Trying to make a living, the best way they knew
In a land of struggle, where time's never at hand
They work hard and hustle, just to make a stand
